wikipedia_page.main: Joshua James Bohannon (born 9 April 1997) is an English cricketer. He made his List A debut for Lancashire in the 2018 Royal London One-Day Cup on 25 May 2018. He made his Twenty20 debut for Lancashire in the 2018 t20 Blast on 3 August 2018. He made his first-class debut for Lancashire in the 2018 County Championship on 17 August 2018.
